# Loops
As with conditionals, there are two syntactic options for loops, braces or colon.

```
//Braces
for($i = 0; $i <= 10; $i++) {
  echo $i;
}

//Colon
<?php for($i = 0; $i <= 10; $i++) : ?>
  <p><?= $i ?></p>
<?php endfor ?>

```
